      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i'm just so tired of being in hospitals and it's so expensive here... plus i was feeling fine right before the flight ended. its probably just the caffeine and all the stress from the trip. how can i tell if it's actually an emergency vs just my anxiety acting up? like what are the real signs?",
